The paper discusses the use of heat map visualizations for enhancing search term recommendations, which is a common topic in information retrieval (cs.IR) and digital libraries (cs.DL). The paper also focuses on the use of visualizations for knowledge discovery, which is relevant to human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Finally, the paper discusses the use of indexing vocabularies, which is relevant to computational linguistics (cs.CL) and cybernetics (cs.CY).
